      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 9 article about attitudes toward race among police officers in Harlem</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on July 9 about attitudes toward race among police officers in Harlem misstated the date of the killing of an unarmed black man, Amadou Diallo, by four policemen in the Bronx (an incident that aroused differing reactions along racial lines). It occurred on Feb. 4, 1999, not in 1998.</p>
      </block>
